Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Not on the sofa.}Ne na pohovce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{On a day like this...}V den jako je tenhle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll take my time with you on the bed.}Vychutnám si tě v posteli.
